title: Car Seat Headrest’s Will Toledo Talks Smash Mouth Plans
text: The beautiful modern love story of Smash Mouth and Car Seat Headrest continues! Way back in August, Smash Mouth took to Twitter to extoll the virtues of " Drunk Drivers/Killer Whales ," and last week, both parties seemed pretty interested in the idea of covering each other's songs for a sure-to-be-incredible collaborative split EP . More »
